3.00	Ken_Brown_(filmmaker)	Ken Brown (filmmaker)	Ken Brown (March 12, 1944, Dayton, Ohio) is an American filmmaker, photographer, cartoonist, and designer. He grew up in Amherst, Massachusetts, relocated to Cambridge, Massachusetts, and currently lives in New York City. He has directed dozens of animations, experimental films and video documentaries over the last four decades.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/06/Ppie.jpg
